Package: simplesigs
Title: Extremely lightweight mutational signature processing tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lovelace", "Luquette", , "lovelace_luquette@hms.harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Lightweight factor definitions that enable processing of single base substitution (SBS)
    and insertion/deletion (ID) mutational signatures and utilities for plotting with standard
    layouts and colors.
